msgid ""
"Below the user has also adjust Azimuth to reduce the error further. Now the "
"error is very low and the process is done. The user should press the stop "
"button."
msgstr ""
"A sota l'usuari també ha ajustat l'azimut per a reduir l'error. Ara l'error "
"és molt baix i el procés ha acabat. L'usuari hauria de prémer el botó "
"d'aturar."

